<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F9F9F9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #cedcd3;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #D7EAD9;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #161817;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #161817;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .team {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .member {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 250px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .member img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .member h3 {
            margin: 10px 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .member p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #666;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 40px;

        }

        @media(max-width: 600px) {
            .team {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>


<div class="container">
    <h1>About Cloth Shop</h1>
    <p>Cloth Shop is dedicated to providing high-quality, stylish clothing for all ages. Our mission is to offer products that combine comfort, durability, and fashion. We believe in sustainable practices and ensure that every piece of clothing we sell is crafted with care and responsibility.</p>
    <p>Whether you are looking for casual wear, office outfits, or trendy fashion pieces, Cloth Shop has something for everyone. Our designs are inspired by global trends while keeping comfort and practicality in mind.</p>

    <h2 style="text-align:center; margin-top: 40px; color: #161817;">Meet Our Team</h2>
    <div class="team">
        <div class="member">
            <img src="images/collection-banner.jpg" alt="Team Member">
            <h3>Jane Doe</h3>
            <p>Founder & Designer - Passionate about fashion and sustainability.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member">
            <img src="images/insta-item6.jpg" alt="Team Member">
            <h3>John Smith</h3>
            <p>Marketing Head - Focused on bringing the best style to our customers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member">
            <img src="images/insta-item2.jpg" alt="Team Member">
            <h3>Emily Lee</h3>
            <p>Operations Manager - Ensures smooth delivery and customer satisfaction.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


</body>
</html>
